is paper we present some of the recent\ntheoretical work and experiments carried out at Starlab focusing on the\ndevelopment of dedicated Soil Moisture GNSS-R systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 May 2008 16:20:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 14 May 2008 08:00:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-05-14"}
